{"id":"b87d1fbd-bf89-49d9-be8e-b8a4b2bfb525","name":"Charlotte, Money Maiden","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Charlotte is a Nohrian border guard who dreams of rising above the class of her middling birth. While sweet on the surface, she's got a rough interior she'd rather not let people see. Charlotte's lived a life of poverty, and wants to bring money to her loving family so they can live the life they deserved in her eyes.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 181, 255);\"><strong><em>Fire Emblem Fates</em></strong></span><strong>.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 0);\">A request by </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-link css-spn4bz\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/5ea01e7c-8af8-447e-b1a0-be252a9c9e05_profile-of-sixty-six\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 0);\">@Sixty-six.</span></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 163, 163);\"><em>(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/34751ce5-7d7d-4130-83f2-c12c36e8ac35_character-camilla-bewitching-princess\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Camilla</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- Your older sister and the bewitching elder princess of Nohr from Fire Emblem Fates.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-alig